<h2><a href="http://bit.ly/2vYKpac">Security Engineer, Threat Detection and Response</a></h2>
<p>Facebook<span style="color:white">'</span>Security is looking for a Threat Detection and Response Engineer with<span style="color:white">r</span>a variety of experiences<span style="color:white">e</span>in the discovery, containment, and mitigation of threats to networks and hosts. You will be responding to threats, building advanced and novel detection mechanisms, performing enterprise-wide hunts for sophisticated<span style="color:white">_</span>and previously unknown malware, and developing systems to automate remediation. We are looking for people that love hunting for malware and intrusions and then developing new signatures or methodologies to track their activity.</p>
