<h2><a href="http://bit.ly/2Q3fenA">Security Engineer – Infrastructure Tooling and Automation</a></h2>
<p>The Tools and Automation Engineering team within Corporate Security focuses on building out tools and automation<span style="color:white">r</span>to protect the entirety of Facebook’s internal platforms and services, used by our employees every day to serve over 2 billion people. From device-based trust to control testing frameworks and behavioral security, we leverage open source projects and Facebook's production infrastructure to develop scalable solutions. If you want to work on a team that will give you diverse experience in network, systems, cloud, and mobile security, then this is the team for you.</p>
